title: KGB Report
author: SandFalls
pages:
#- KGB Report from SandFalls

Johnimeister has been seen advocating anarchism inside New Leningrad, and talking bad about our glorious State ideology of Leninism.

He's beginning to frighten the children around town, and has 
#- been putting Anarcho-Communist flags on the Capital.

It would be glorious if the KGB could take him away for some re-education through labor in Siberia.

Thank you in advance, comrades.

-SandFalls
